@@TJvRadioButton.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the radio button is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to True to provide visual feedback about which item is under the mouse; the font
  specified by HotTrackFont is used for the radio button text. When HotTrack is False, there is no
  visual feedback when the mouse passes over the radio button.
See Also
  TJvRadioButton.HotGlyph, TJvRadioButton.HotTrackFont, TJvRadioButton.OnMouseEnter,
  TJvRadioButton.OnMouseLeave

